                        Distributed By <a class="border-bottom" href="https://themewagon.com" target="_blank">ThemeWagon</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-end">
                        <div class="footer-menu">
                            <a href="">Home</a>
                            <a href="">Cookies</a>
